  & #onetrust-banner-sdk:focus {
    outline: unset;
    outline-offset: unset;
    outline-color: unset;
    outline-width: unset;
  }
  & #onetrust-banner-sdk {
    & .ot-sdk-container {
      color: var(--ot-color-black);
      & .ot-sdk-row > div {
        max-width: 1200px;
      }
      & .ot-sdk-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        & * {
          font-family: inherit;
          -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
          font-size: 1rem;
          line-height: 24px;
          @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
            font-size: 14px;
          }
        }
        & #onetrust-group-container {
          @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
            width: 90%;
          }
          & #onetrust-policy {
            & h2,
            h3 {
              font-weight: 600;
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 24px;
              margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
            margin: 3rem 0 3rem;
            @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
              margin: 1.5rem 0 1.25rem;
              h3 {
                margin-top: 16px;
              }
              h2,
              h3 {
                font-size: 14px;
              }
            }
            & #onetrust-policy-text {
              border-right: unset;
              padding-bottom: 0;
              & .ot-tcf2-vendor-count {
                font-weight: 400;
              }
              & .ot-cookie-policy-link {
                font-weight: 400;
              }
            }
            & #onetrust-policy-text,
            .ot-dpd-container .ot-dpd-desc {
              font-weight: 400;
            }
            & .ot-dpd-container {
              & .onetrust-vendors-list-handler {
                font-weight: 400;
                text-decoration: underline;
              }
            }
          }
        }
        & #onetrust-button-group-parent {
          width: 82.67%;
          position: static;
          transform: unset;
          margin-left: unset;
          @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
            width: 90%;
            background: #ffffff;
            position: sticky;
            bottom: 0;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            top: unset;
            left: unset;
          }
          & #onetrust-button-group {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
              display: flex;
              flex-direction: column;

              & #onetrust-accept-btn-handler,
              #onetrust-reject-all-handler,
              #onetrust-pc-btn-handler {
                margin-bottom: 12px;
              }
            }
            & button {
              padding: unset;
              margin: unset;
              height: 3rem;
            }

            & #onetrust-accept-btn-handler {
              order: 3;
              grid-column: 7;
              background-color: var(--ot--color-green);
              border-color: var(--ot--color-green);
              background-image: none;
              border: 2px solid var(--ot--color-green);
              border-radius: 2px;
              box-sizing: border-box;
              color: #fff;
              cursor: pointer;
              font-family: inherit;
              font-size: 1rem;
              font-weight: bold;
              line-height: 24px;
              min-width: 200px;
              text-align: center;
              transition: background-color 0.2s ease 0s, color 0.2s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;
              @media (max-width: 992px) {
                order: 1;
              }
            }
            & #onetrust-accept-btn-handler:hover {
              background: var(--ot--color-green-hover);
              border-color: var(--ot--color-green-hover);
            }
            & #onetrust-reject-all-handler {
              order: 1;
              background: none;
              border: 2px solid var(--ot-color-black);
              border-radius: 2px;
              box-sizing: border-box;
              color: var(--ot-color-black);
              cursor: pointer;
              font-family: inherit;
              font-size: 1rem;
              font-weight: bold;
              line-height: 24px;
              margin-right: 0;
              min-width: 200px;
              text-align: center;
              transition: background-color 0.2s ease 0s, color 0.2s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;
              @media (max-width: 992px) {
                order: 2;
              }
            }
            & #onetrust-reject-all-handler:hover {
              border-color: var(--ot--color-gray);
              color: var(--ot--color-gray);
            }
            & #onetrust-pc-btn-handler {
              order: 2;
              font-size: 1rem;
              text-align: center;
              @media (max-width: 992px) {
                order: 3;
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

  padding: 0 !important;

            :root {
  --ot-color-black: #404040;
  --ot--color-blue: #3860be;
  --ot--color-gray: #333333; /* hover color for buttons */
  --ot--color-green: #f06c00; /* color for accept all button */
  --ot--color-green-hover: #e55000; /* hover color for accept all button */
}

.ot-pc-refuse-all-handler {
  background-color: white !important;
  color: var(--ot-color-black) !important;
}

#onetrust-pc-sdk {
  min-width: 574px;
  max-width: 574px;
  @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
    min-width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  & .ot-pc-header {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-bottom: unset;
  }
  & #ot-pc-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    & * {
      font-family: inherit;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 24px;
      color: var(--ot-color-black);
      min-height: unset;
      @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
    & *:focus {
      outline: none;
      border: none;
    }
    & h2,
    h3 {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
    & > button {
      padding: unset;
      margin: unset;
      margin-right: unset !important;
      /* margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important; */
      max-width: unset;
    }
    & button:hover {
      border-color: var(--ot--color-gray);
      color: var(--ot--color-gray);
    }
    & #accept-recommended-btn-handler {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
      display: flex !important;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background-color: var(--ot--color-green);
      border-color: var(--ot--color-green);
      border: 2px solid var(--ot--color-green);
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
      line-height: 1;
      min-width: 200px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease 0s, color 0.2s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;
      padding: 15px 30px;
    }
    & #accept-recommended-btn-handler:hover {
      background: var(--ot--color-green-hover);
      border-color: var(--ot--color-green-hover);
    }
    & #ot-pc-desc {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    & .ot-sdk-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      & #ot-category-title {
        padding: unset;
        margin: unset;
      }
      & > div {
        border: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
        /* padding: 12px; */
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      & .ot-cat-item {
        & .ot-cat-header {
          font-weight: 400;
        }
        & .ot-tgl {
          & input:checked + .ot-switch .ot-switch-nob {
            background-color: var(--ot--color-blue);
          }
          & .ot-switch-nob {
            background-color: #8c8c8c;
          }
        }
        & .ot-plus-minus {
          & span {
            background: var(--ot-color-black);
          }
        }
        & .ot-acc-grpcntr.ot-acc-txt {
          background-color: #fff;
        }
      }
      &.ot-cat-item:first-of-type {
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
      }
    }
  }
  .ot-pc-footer {
    background: white;
    z-index: 10;
    border-top: unset;
    & .ot-btn-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      & * {
        font-family: inherit;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        font-size: 1rem;
        max-width: none;
        @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
          font-size: 14px;
        }
      }
      & button.ot-pc-refuse-all-handler,
      button.save-preference-btn-handler {
        margin-top: unset !important;
        margin-right: unset !important;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border: 2px solid var(--ot-color-black);
      }
      & button:nth-of-type(2) {
        margin-top: 1.5rem !important;
      }
      & button.ot-pc-refuse-all-handler:hover {
        border-color: var(--ot--color-gray) !important;
        color: var(--ot--color-gray) !important;
      }
      & button.save-preference-btn-handler:hover {
        background: var(--ot--color-gray);
        border-color: var(--ot--color-gray);
      }
    }
  }
}
